      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POWER VALLEY (2) goes very well over this track and trip including three wins. Scored by 6 lengths last time (20.02) in a Mix over 350m at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. WORDS OF WISDOM (8) jumped from a squeeze box last start but was quickly into stride and led throughout to score (20.03) at this track in a Mix over 350m. Likely to be in the finish. COSMIC CASPER (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.43) at this track behind POWER VALLEY in a Mix. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can measure up. ZIPPING BJORN (3) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
